":"","content_rendered":"","last_modified":1634955215,"replies":15,"id":809970},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_large.png?m=1634260728","name":"windows","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_normal.png?m=1634260728","title":"Windows","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows","topics":2352,"footer":"","header":"Windows, not walls.","title_alternative":"Windows","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1634260728","stars":778,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":360,"parent_node_name":"os"},"member":{"username":"Knuth","website":null,"github":null,"psn":null,"avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/aea488b5566c4ef8fc574e316fb04ef2?s=24&d=retro","bio":null,"url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Knuth","tagline":null,"twitter":null,"created":1589012414,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/aea488b5566c4ef8fc574e316fb04ef2?s=24&d=retro","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/aea488b5566c4ef8fc574e316fb04ef2?s=24&d=retro","location":null,"btc":null,"id":488565},"last_reply_by":"Knuth","last_touched":1634973862,"title":"请教一个 WSL2 上代理的问题","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/809967","created":1634954632,"deleted":0,"content":"因为 windows 分配给 wsl2 的 IP 是动态变化的，所以我在.bashrc 设置了如下环境变量，我想用`curl cip.cc`检测终端是不走代理，但返回的是国内当地的 ip 地址\r\n```\r\nexport host_ip=$(cat /etc/resolv.conf |grep -oP '(?<=nameserver\\ ).*')\r\nexport https_proxy=\"http://${host_ip}:7890\"\r\nexport http_proxy=\"http://${host_ip}:7890\"\r\nexport all_proxy=\"http://${host_ip}:7890\"\r\n```\r\n\r\n所以请教下大家，终端走代理的正确姿势该怎么操作呢？","content_rendered":"<p>因为 windows 分配给 wsl2 的 IP 是动态变化的，所以我在.bashrc 设置了如下环境变量，我想用<code>curl <a href=\"http://cip.cc\" rel=\"nofollow\">cip.cc</a></code>检测终端是不走代理，但返回的是国内当地的 ip 地址</p>\n<pre><code>export host_ip=$(cat /etc/resolv.conf |grep -oP '(?&lt;=nameserver\\ ).*')\nexport https_proxy=\"http://${host_ip}:7890\"\nexport http_proxy=\"http://${host_ip}:7890\"\nexport all_proxy=\"http://${host_ip}:7890\"\n</code></pre>\n<p>所以请教下大家，终端走代理的正确姿势该怎么操作呢？</p>\n","last_modified":1634959653,"replies":15,"id":809967},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_large.png?m=1620107025","name":"bb","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_normal.png?m=1620107025","title":"宽带症候群","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb","topics":9849,"footer":"","header":"网速很重要。比快更快。","title_alternative":"Broadband Symptom Complex","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1620107025","stars":5179,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":108,"parent_node_name":"geek"},"member":{"username":"yoa1q7y","website":"","github":"","psn":"","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7ce3/0f00/115394_mini.png?m=1622803863","bio":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/yoa1q7y","tagline":"","twitter":"","created":1430838911,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7ce3/0f00/115394_mini.png?m=1622803863","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7ce3/0f00/115394_mini.png?m=1622803863","location":"","btc":"","id":115394},"last_reply_by":"titanium98118","last_touched":1634970026,"title":"想知道旁路网关(旁路由)模式有什么样的缺点？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/809992","created":1634963292,"deleted":0,"content":"刚开始接触软路由，大多数文章写的模式是软路由作为主路由，负责连接光猫 + 拨号，然后将硬路由作为 AP 提供无线信号，这样局域网内的所有设备都可以使用软路由上的插件\r\n\r\n昨天试了一下旁路网关模式，硬路由依然负责连接光猫 + 拨号，然后在硬路由上设置默认网关为旁路由的 IP 地址，也可以达到所有设备使用软路由的插件，无需在设备上单独设置\r\n\r\n也就是说，这两种模式效果似乎是一样的，所以想知道旁路网关模式有什么缺点呢？看文章说旁路网关模式，如果旁路由挂了，所有设备就都无法上网了，可是，软路由作为主路由模式如果挂了不是一样导致无法上网么？\r\n\r\n附上腹语哥关于旁路网关的视频\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w7rwNF2Q3lM","content_rendered":"刚开始接触软路由，大多数文章写的模式是软路由作为主路由，负责连接光猫 + 拨号，然后将硬路由作为 AP 提供无线信号，这样局域网内的所有设备都可以使用软路由上的插件<br /><br />昨天试了一下旁路网关模式，硬路由依然负责连接光猫 + 拨号，然后在硬路由上设置默认网关为旁路由的 IP 地址，也可以达到所有设备使用软路由的插件，无需在设备上单独设置<br /><br />也就是说，这两种模式效果似乎是一样的，所以想知道旁路网关模式有什么缺点呢？看文章说旁路网关模式，如果旁路由挂了，所有设备就都无法上网了，可是，软路由作为主路由模式如果挂了不是一样导致无法上网么？<br /><br />附上腹语哥关于旁路网关的视频<br /><div class=\"embedded_video_wrapper\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/w7rwNF2Q3lM\" class=\"e