ull,"github":null,"psn":null,"avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8941/16d6/496485_mini.png?m=1593228385","bio":null,"url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Anekys","tagline":null,"twitter":null,"created":1593227820,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8941/16d6/496485_mini.png?m=1593228385","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8941/16d6/496485_mini.png?m=1593228385","location":null,"btc":null,"id":496485},"last_reply_by":"LinShiG0ng","last_touched":1634974439,"title":"作为一个大三计科生,该为以后选择什么方向?","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/809974","created":1634955990,"deleted":0,"content":"垃圾本科的大三计科生(还是专接本的),不知道以后就业该选什么了,求大佬解惑.\r\n\r\n本身对爬虫,逆向,渗透这种的都比较感兴趣,但是实际上接触的比较多的还是爬虫,水平不高,目前正在学猿人学的 JS 逆向题目.自己也试着在 BOSS 上面过一些爬虫岗,不过看到的都是要精通爬虫还得擅长数据分析(Numpy,pandas,matplotlib 等),目前这一块还处于仅仅是知道模块名字而已.\r\n\r\n不知道到底要不要坚持爬虫这一块,我在 Boss 上看,北京的爬虫岗有的甚至还不如 Web 前端,或者做 Web 给的多.但是实际上又不是很想作 Web,想要钱,也想要追寻自己的兴趣,感觉自己属于典型的又菜又爱玩.但是迫于现实的情况有点纠结到底是继续研究爬虫,还是利用现在的时间抓紧学学其他的,好在大四实习时能够转到其他方向.","content_rendered":"垃圾本科的大三计科生(还是专接本的),不知道以后就业该选什么了,求大佬解惑.<br /><br />本身对爬虫,逆向,渗透这种的都比较感兴趣,但是实际上接触的比较多的还是爬虫,水平不高,目前正在学猿人学的 JS 逆向题目.自己也试着在 BOSS 上面过一些爬虫岗,不过看到的都是要精通爬虫还得擅长数据分析(Numpy,pandas,matplotlib 等),目前这一块还处于仅仅是知道模块名字而已.<br /><br />不知道到底要不要坚持爬虫这一块,我在 Boss 上看,北京的爬虫岗有的甚至还不如 Web 前端,或者做 Web 给的多.但是实际上又不是很想作 Web,想要钱,也想要追寻自己的兴趣,感觉自己属于典型的又菜又爱玩.但是迫于现实的情况有点纠结到底是继续研究爬虫,还是利用现在的时间抓紧学学其他的,好在大四实习时能够转到其他方向.","last_modified":1634955990,"replies":13,"id":809974},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_large.png?m=1620107025","name":"bb","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_normal.png?m=1620107025","title":"宽带症候群","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb","topics":9848,"footer":"","header":"网速很重要。比快更快。","title_alternative":"Broadband Symptom Complex","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1620107025","stars":5179,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":108,"parent_node_name":"geek"},"member":{"username":"qdwang","website":"","github":null,"psn":null,"avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4be3/f330/40309_mini.png?m=1557747990","bio":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/qdwang","tagline":"","twitter":null,"created":1370598288,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4be3/f330/40309_mini.png?m=1557747990","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4be3/f330/40309_mini.png?m=1557747990","location":"","btc":null,"id":40309},"last_reply_by":"ScepterZ","last_touched":1634971224,"title":"请教一下，关于光猫，桥接， dmz， ap 的性能问题","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/809966","created":1634954474,"deleted":0,"content":"结构 1：internet----光猫（ PPPOE ）---<dmz>---无线路由------PC\r\n\r\n结构 2：internet----光猫---<桥接>---无线路由（ PPPOE ）------PC\r\n\r\n结构 3：internet----光猫（ PPPOE ）---无线路由（ AP 模式）------PC\r\n\r\n\r\n现在家里的是 sdn 网关，要改桥接比较麻烦，得师傅上门。\r\n\r\n所以想请问一下，结构 1 和结构 3，哪个性能会好一些呢？\r\n\r\n光猫型号是 HG2821T-U，路由型号 XDR3250\r\n\r\n另外，有什么比较好的测试整体路由性能的方法？\r\n\r\n谢谢","content_rendered":"<p>结构 1：internet----光猫（ PPPOE ）---&lt;dmz&gt;---无线路由------PC</p>\n<p>结构 2：internet----光猫---&lt;桥接&gt;---无线路由（ PPPOE ）------PC</p>\n<p>结构 3：internet----光猫（ PPPOE ）---无线路由（ AP 模式）------PC</p>\n<p>现在家里的是 sdn 网关，要改桥接比较麻烦，得师傅上门。</p>\n<p>所以想请问一下，结构 1 和结构 3，哪个性能会好一些呢？</p>\n<p>光猫型号是 HG2821T-U，路由型号 XDR3250</p>\n<p>另外，有什么比较好的测试整体路由性能的方法？</p>\n<p>谢谢</p>\n","last_modified":1634954527,"replies":13,"id":809966},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df7f/28ac/791_large.png?m=1563424621","name":"fe","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df7f/28ac/791_normal.png?m=1563424621","title":"前端开发","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/fe","topics":2321,"footer":"","header":"","title_alternative":"Frontend","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df7f/28ac/791_mini.png?m=1563424621","stars":1103,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":791,"parent_node_name":"programmer"},"member":{"username":"wzx155","website":"","github":null,"psn":null,"avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d76a/28c8/489744_mini.png?m=1608095013","bio":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/wzx155","tagline":"","twitter":null,"created":1589540722,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d76a/28c8/489744_mini.png?m=1608095013","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d76a/28c8/489744_mini.png?m=1608095013","location":"","btc":null,"id":489744},"last_reply_by":"dengshen","last_touched":1634986644,"title":"今天测试说网页登录的时候如果密码输入错误浏览器不要弹出记住密码，如果输入正确浏览器弹出记住密码，请问各位大佬这个功能怎么实现啊？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/810019","created":1634975507,"deleted":0,"content":"","content_rendered":"","last_modified":1634975507,"replies":12,"id":810019},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_large.png?m=1634260728","name":"windows","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_normal.png?m=1634260728","title":"Windows","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows","topics":2352,"footer":"","header":"Windows, not walls.","title_alternative":"Windows","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1634260728","stars":778,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":360,"parent_node_name":"os"},"member":{"username":"h82258652","website":"","github":"h82258652","psn":"","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/070a9dbef93f261e5d29886992bd699c?s=24&d=retro","bio":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/h82258652","tagline":"","twitter":"","created":1521272522,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/070a9dbef93f261e5d29886992bd699c?s=24&d=retro","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/070a9dbef93f261e5d29886992bd699c?s=24&d=retro","location":"","btc":"","id":300943},"last_reply_by":"GrayXu","last_touched":1634982496,"title":"为什么 MS 不继续发展 AOW，而是弄 WSA？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/809996","created":1634964681,"deleted":0,"content":"AOW 是以前 Windows 10 Mobile 那个，运行时转译字节码，然后部分功能例如文件存储、摄像头调用桥接到 Windows 10 Mobile 系统上。当时用 Lumia 535 有幸试过一下，1G ram 的机子运行比较简单的 apk，跑起来还算挺流畅的。\r\n现在 Windows 11 这个 WSA 就是个虚拟机，也就将虚拟机里面的消息通知接入到了 Win11 系统。用公司的电脑体验了一下，启动虚拟机就占了 900 多 M 的内存了。\r\n\r\n比起虚拟机的方案，AOW 的方案不是更佳么？虽然工作量应该要多不少，但是技术上当时也验证过了，搞不懂为什么 MS 不继续发展 AOW 。","content_rendered":"AOW 是以前 Windows 10 Mobile 那个，运行时转译字节码，然后部分功能例如文件存储、摄像头调用桥接到 Windows 10 Mobile 系统上。当时用 Lumia 535 有幸试过一下，1G ram 的机子运行比较简单的 apk，跑起来还算挺流畅的。<br />现在 Windows 11 这个 WSA 就是个虚拟机，也就将虚拟机里面的消息通知接入到了 Win11 系统。用公司的电脑体验了一下，启动虚拟机就占了 900 多 M 的内存了。<br /><br />比起虚拟机的方案，AOW 的方案不是更佳么？虽然工作量应该要多不少，但是技术上当时也验证过了，搞不懂为什么 MS 不继续发展 AOW 。","last_modified":1634964681,"replies":11,"id":809996},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_large.png?m=1629391403","name":"create","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_normal.png?m=1629391403","title":"分享创造","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/create","topics":16833,"footer":"","header":"欢迎你在这里发布自己的最新作品！","title_alternative":"Create","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1629391403","stars":4080,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":17,"parent_node_name":"geek"},"member":{"username":"isbase","website":"","github":"","psn":"","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/faefb60d3617d93d693d128fa99a5737?s=24&d=retro","bio":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/isbase","tagline":"","twitter":"","created":1402420419,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/faefb60d3617d93d693d128fa99a5737?s=24&d=retro","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/faefb60d3617d93d693d128fa99a5737?s=24&d=retro","location":"","btc":"","id":64727},"last_reply_by":"q197","last_touched":1634969496,"title":"我写了个工具，找到了国内 Xbox 下载最快的节点","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/809975","created":1634956701,"deleted":0,"content":"[https://baiyun.me/fix-slow-xbox-download-speed]( https://baiyun.me/fix-slow-xbox-download-speed)\r\n\r\n![Xbox 下载速度排序]( https://i.isbase.me/resource/uPic/20211023043645-83pGdi.jpg)","content_rendered":"<p><a href=\"https://baiyun.me/fix-slow-xbox-download-speed\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://baiyun.me/fix-slow-xbox-download-speed</a></p>\n<p><img alt=\"Xbox 下载速度排序\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.isbase.me/resource/uPic/20211023043645-83pGdi.jpg\"/></p>\n","last_modified":1634956883,"replies":11,"id":809975},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_large.png?m=1633314282","name":"macos","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_normal.png?m=1633314282","title":"macOS","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/macos","topics":17178,"footer":"<a href=\"/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 等 <a href=\"/go/apple\">Apple</a> 公司设计的计算机所运行的操作系统。<a href=\"/go/idev\">iOS</a> 的基础。","header":"The world’s most advanced desktop operating system.","title_alternative":"macOS","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_mini.png?m=1633314282","stars":4424,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":22,"parent_node_name":"os"},"member":{"username":"moweiraul","website":null,"github":null,"psn":null,"avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/496710bb309b1ce7ce0cabcc8a1af7ff?s=24&d=retro","bio":null,"url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/moweiraul","tagline":null,"twitter":null,"created":1575072070,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/496710bb309b1ce7ce0cabcc8a1af7ff?s=24&d=retro","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/496710bb309b1ce7ce0cabcc8a1af7ff?s=24&d=retro","location":null,"btc":null,"id":456400},"last_reply_by":"banjintaohua","last_touched":1634959318,"title":"U2720Q 搭配 MAC，显示器颜色设置到底要怎么调","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/809959","created":1634950850,"content":"1 、在启用 hdr 模式的情况下\r\n\r\n显示器设置 display HDR，系统开启 HDR，这个 hdr 是全局的，看视频确实惊艳，但是桌面日常使用，也是 hdr 的，会导致颜色很怪，并且颜色有些发暗发灰\r\n\r\n如何能配置，让其只在视频时启用，而不是全局启用\r\n\r\n2 、在非 HDR 模式下\r\n\r\n1. 显示器颜色设置为“标准”，颜色会过饱和\r\n2. 显示器设置为“dci-p3”，颜色又会发绿\r\n3. 设置为 srgb 又不甘心，明明显示器能支持 95%的 p3\r\n\r\n另外在系统中的色彩文件，还有好多种，这个要和显示器的设置中如何搭配，才能尽可能实现到 macbook 屏幕的那种观感，或者说，才是正确的颜色配置\r\n\r\n折腾了半天了，不是学色彩的，对各种色彩设置确实蒙圈。\r\n\r\n还请帮忙指点下","content_rendered":"<p>1 、在启用 hdr 模式的情况下</p>\n<p>显示器设置 display HDR，系统开启 HDR，这个 hdr 是全局的，看视频确实惊艳，但是桌面日常使用，也是 hdr 的，会导致颜色很怪，并且颜色有些发暗发灰</p>\n<p>如何能配置，让其只在视频时启用，而不是全局启用</p>\n<p>2 、在非 HDR 模式下</p>\n<ol>\n<li>显示器颜色设置为“标准”，颜色会过饱和</li>\n<li>显示器设置为“dci-p3”，颜色又会发绿</li>\n<li>设置为 srgb 又不甘心，明明显示器能支持 95%的 p3</li>\n</ol>\n<p>另外在系统中的色彩文件，还有好多种，这个要和显示器的设置中如何搭配，才能尽可能实现到 macbook 屏幕的那种观感，或者说，才是正确的颜色配置</p>\n<p>折腾了半天了，不是学色彩的，对各种色彩设置确实蒙圈。</p>\n<p>还请帮忙指点下</p>\n","last_modified":1634950930,"replies":11,"id":809959},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1634712722","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1634712722","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":46020,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1634712722","stars":7554,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"username":"meisen","website":"","github":"","psn":"","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ca1b/c8a9/476364_mini.png?m=1628751594","bio":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/meisen","tagline":"","twitter":"","created":1584072591,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ca1b/c8a9/476364_mini.png?m=1628751594","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ca1b/c8a9/476364_mini.png?m=1628751594","location":"","btc":"","id":476364},"last_reply_by":"theprimone","last_touched":1634987569,"title":"程序员 5 年坚持制作免费教程造福百万学生","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/810045","created":1634983460,"deleted":0,"content":"标题为微博热搜看到，此人 B 站：[/165659472]( https://space.bilibili.com/165659472) ，虽然我不是程序员，简单了解下值得竖大拇指👍🏻，不知道 V 站有没有他账号。\r\n\r\n![]( https://i.imgur.com/eRBMgoG.png)","content_rendered":"<p>标题为微博热搜看到，此人 B 站：<a href=\"https://space.bilibili.com/165659472\" rel=\"nofollow\">/165659472</a> ，虽然我不是程序员，简单了解下值得竖大拇指👍🏻，不知道 V 站有没有他账号。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eRBMgoG.png\"/></p>\n","last_modified":1634983460,"replies":10,"id":810045}]